5:["$","p",null,{"children":["QuickTransfer isn't just for sending files to other people; it's also a fantastic tool for moving data between your own devices. Need to get a photo from your phone to your laptop? Just use ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"QuickTransfer"}],". It’s faster than email and more universal than most proprietary \"airdrop\" features."]}]
